name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bhai Kya Kar Raha Hai Tu

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension shows 'bhai kya kar raha hai tu' meme when user opens a block-listed website.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension shows 'bhai kya kar raha hai tu' meme when user opens a block-listed website. It is a website-blocker built for fun.

Create and Manage your own block-list.
Set a custom-image which is shown when you visit a block-listed website.
